HEADWORD: Self-educated
<hw>Self`-ed"u*ca`ted</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Educated by
one's own efforts, without instruction, or without pecuniary assistance
from others.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

